original_title: Final Curtain: Part 9 - The Legend Continues
overview: Ethan Carver returns to Taft. One year after his Manhattan massacre, Ethan's body has disappeared. Rumors that he is lurking somewhere in Taft have spread throughout the town. nearby, counselors are getting a campsite ready for the summer. But suspicious townspeople are warning then about Ethan's inevitable return. As the daylight dims, Ethan returns to the camp and no one is safe as he tears the place apart. But someone else is at the camp, someone with a sinister motive, someone who seems to be helping Ethan carry out his terrifying mission.
title: Final Curtain: Part 9 - The Legend Continues
